Johannesburg – Don’t panic if you forgot Father’s Day as there are loads of last-minute fabulous gifts you can give to the love of your life, your Father. We sourced the following, some free and some worth every cent. FIT FOR A KING’S BAR Treat your dad with some class with this sexy and delicious cognac
Bisquit & Dubouche VSOP for R719.99 or
Bisquit & Dobuoche VS R449.99 available from reputable Liquor Stores. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-75353" src="http://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Cognac-480x800.png" alt="" width="480" height="800" srcset="https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Cognac-480x800.png 480w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Cognac-150x250.png 150w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Cognac-696x1160.png 696w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Cognac-252x420.png 252w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Cognac.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px" /> UPDATE HIS WARDROBE We love good looking comfort, get him any of these, Vans EVDNT R1 999, Vans SK 8 Hite Tartan Daze for R1 299 all from street gym. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-75354" src="http://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-800x549.jpg" alt="" width="696" height="478" srcset="https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-800x549.jpg 800w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-250x171.jpg 250w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-768x527.jpg 768w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-218x150.jpg 218w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-436x300.jpg 436w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-696x477.jpg 696w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-1068x733.jpg 1068w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-612x420.jpg 612w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans-100x70.jpg 100w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Vans.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px" /> SAVOURY AND SWEET DELIGHTS Starbucks is also a great place to take Dad this Father’s Day because their breakfasts and lunches are spectacular and I love that they have food and beverage pairing curated just for Dad. SAVE THE PLANET Save the environment and show dad you care by getting him an eco-friendly sustainable product by WWF SA. We love the T-shirt made from recycled bottles, a zero-waste razor kit and a cozy Panda hoodie that will ensure Dad is warm and our natural heritage is looked after. Find them by clicking here. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-75356" src="http://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/FATHERS-DAY-WWF-581x800.jpg" alt="" width="581" height="800" /> FREE TASTING AND FLASHY CARS If you are low on funds, simple take your dad to Hyde Park Corner and view the supercars from Future Exotics and sample free coffees from Asmara Coffee from Tribeca, Kimbo Coffee from J B Rivers and please tell me what the Mushroom Coffee from Health Works tastes like. Oh, don’t forget they have Whiskey tasting too. ART MEETS GIN We love the Musgrave Original Limited edition(R430.00) because its limited making it perfect for the man in your life. Get your hands on a limited edition Musgrave Eleven inspired by Jasmine Jagger this Father’s Day. Best served with a cooling slice of cucumber, the zest of pink grapefruit and rosemary or peppery bunch of basil. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-75357" src="http://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-689x800.jpg" alt="" width="689" height="800" srcset="https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-689x800.jpg 689w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-215x250.jpg 215w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-768x892.jpg 768w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-1322x1536.jpg 1322w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-696x809.jpg 696w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-1068x1241.jpg 1068w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin-361x420.jpg 361w, https://sundayworld.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Gin.jpg 1102w" sizes="(max-width: 689px) 100vw, 689px" /> GIN FOR DAD Try Flowstones’ Snuffbox Gin which gets its name from its hard shelled fruit with dark and rich, warm flavours get it from reputable Liquor Stores QUICK TREAT FOR DAD 50ml Flowstone Snuff Box Gin
15ml Simple Syrup
15ml Lemon juice
1 Egg white
Nutmeg, cocoa or chocolate powder to garnish METHOD Put Gin, syrup, lemon juice and egg white into a shaker. Shake for 30 seconds then add the ice and shake for another 20 seconds. Keep the ice back and pour into cocktail glasses ensuring you have grated the nutmeg over the foam and added some cocoa. Then serve him. There you have it, you have no reasons to give your old man socks. Happy Father’s Day. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here. Sunday World 